	(text_box "TP4056 board has a common positive battery disconnector, which is not ideal for our use case.\nThe only option is to leave the battery and the related charging circuit floating in respect to everything else (or add a separate UVLO).\nKeep it in mind while probing around."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
